  "1777990": {
    "name": "Ortharion : The Last Battle",
    "steam_appid": 1777990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ortharion: The Last Battle</strong> 是一款单人 hack'n slash RPG，带你沉浸在一个充满秘密的中世纪幻想世界中。选择不同的职业和装备组合，成为最强大的存在，探索广阔的世界，克服所有最具挑战性的任务和强大首领！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/58043d88a487e342c735b57ea90c17d5.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/58043d88a487e342c735b57ea90c17d5.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/58043d88a487e342c735b57ea90c17d5.mp4?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>职业进化：</strong> 从游戏开始时可用的三种职业中选择，随着游戏的进行，逐渐选择新的职业，获得不同的优势，最终可以同时选择三十九种职业中的七种专长，几乎提供无限的可能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/9581a54958fdeca440185c9454e9a864.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/9581a54958fdeca440185c9454e9a864.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/9581a54958fdeca440185c9454e9a864.mp4?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过 350 种可升级法术：</strong> 法术需要被发现和学习，分为六种稀有度，可以升级。学习法术需要特定的属性和职业。法术的效果随后会受到天赋和装备的修改。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/1425ba2bad409eb020675b90b7528bc3.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/1425ba2bad409eb020675b90b7528bc3.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/1425ba2bad409eb020675b90b7528bc3.mp4?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>15 位主要首领等待挑战：</strong> 首领分为两类：普通首领是小挑战，而 15 位主要首领几乎没有容错空间。并不是所有的主要首领都相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索世界：</strong> 通过探索来提升你的角色，发现隐藏在世界中的所有秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/dbcd7e273e8494ba06639e4b052d83d4.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/dbcd7e273e8494ba06639e4b052d83d4.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/dbcd7e273e8494ba06639e4b052d83d4.mp4?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>程序生成的物品：</strong> 每件物品可以具有独特的能力，属于一个套装，包含符文或宝石，使得组合的数量超过其他 hack'n slash 游戏。属性也是随机的，并按等级分配。同时还提供基于消耗品的自定义系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/69b6d9247396bb77da2cecac40822aec.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/69b6d9247396bb77da2cecac40822aec.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>天赋树：</strong> 每个 Ortharion 的碎片为你在天赋树中提供一个点数，进一步个性化你的角色。天赋树是特定于每个职业的，某些天赋可以完全改变游戏玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/3af95e7c47459f9803afbf8c4254dfd9.poster.avif?t=1764701708\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777990/extras/3af95e7c47459f9803afbf8c4254dfd9.webm?t=1764701708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞技模式：</strong> 游戏设计了一个排名系统。你需要积累积分，并可以通过季节性系统将积分与朋友或社区进行比较。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高等级内容：</strong> 参与多种高等级系统，同时参与主线任务、首领竞技场、怪物波次、随机地下城、目标保护等。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 韩语, 日语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
